warning: Lint[5655] This is a cross-boundary edge. Although the callee is accessible to the caller's package pkg1 via __PackageOverride('pkg1'), that package override is load-bearing here: without it the callee stays in package pkg2, which pkg1 cannot reach, so this edge would be an error. This edge prevents removal of the __PackageOverride and SHOULD BE REMOVED. Either move the callee into the caller's package via hg mv, use __RequirePackage (if the whole function should only be invoked from pkg2) or gate this reference via a package check (if this portion of the function is meant to be gated by an environment check). [1]

